PRIVACY POLICY
RESOLUTION GAMES
In this privacy policy (“
Privacy Policy
”), it is described how Resolution Games AB including its affiliates
(“
Resolution Games
”) Processes Personal Data. For more information and/or to exercise rights as a Data Subject, contact information to Resolution Games can be found under Contact Information.
The law in some jurisdictions may provide you with additional rights regarding our use of Personal Data. To learn more about any additional rights that may be applicable to you as a resident of one of these jurisdictions, please see the privacy addendum for your jurisdiction that is attached to this Privacy Policy.
If you are located in California, you have additional rights described in our Privacy Policy Addendum for California Residents
